title: War of the Roses: Palm Trees in New York?
description: Tracy has been dating Kevin for a while but there's a problem, they've still never met in person.  He lives in Seattle and was supposed to come visit recently but his flight got cancelled, which happens, but then Kevin sent Tracy a picture of himself that has her wondering if he might be catfishing her because of what she saw in the background.  We find out on War of the Roses!
